<collectingRegion box="[1306,1387,513,539]" country="China" name="Xizang" pageId="5" pageNumber="587">Xizang</collectingRegion>
Autonomous Prefecture, Southwestern 
<collectingCountry box="[557,628,549,575]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="587">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="587" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,153,647]" pageId="5" pageNumber="587">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,585,611]" pageId="5" pageNumber="587">Etymology.</emphasis>
Gesar is the name of the fearless lord of the legendary kingdom of Ling in Tibetan traditional legend.
</paragraph>
